vote.title: An ordinance ordering a runoff election to be held in the city of Dallas, on Saturday, June 5, 2021, for the purpose of electing Members of the City Council for Places 2, 4, 7, 11, 13 and 14 in which no candidate received a majority of the votes in the general election held Saturday, May 1, 2021 - Financing:  No cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information)
